"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425334","Department for Culture, Media and Sport","false","2015-11-10","<p>I have had no discussions with FIFA officials regarding candidates standing for the FIFA Presidency.</p><blockquote> </blockquote>","Chatham and Aylesford","Tracey Crouch",,"2015-11-10T16:11:35.323Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425334/answer","Biography information for Tracey Crouch","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425334/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/425334/answer",,,,,"10","Culture, Media and Sport","Culture, Media and Sport","2015-11-02","FIFA","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Culture, Media and Sport, what discussions he has had with FIFA officials on the candidacy of Sheikh Salman bin Ebrahim al-Khalifa for FIFA President.","false","Biography information for Helen Goodman","Bishop Auckland","Helen Goodman","14429"
